# Market Analysis and Pricing Strategy

## Executive Summary
The iOS typing tutor market is segmented into gamified apps for kids, rigorous speed-training tools for adults, and general educational platforms. There is a significant opportunity for a modern, high-polish app that bridges the gap between "fun/gamified" and "serious skill building" for a broad age range, utilizing the latest iOS technologies (SwiftUI, Game Center).

